nodes.title: Looper
nodes.label: Looper
nodes.abstract: This film is a futuristic action thriller, a mob invents time travel, which is illegal and will be available only in the black market. If the mob wants to get rid of someone then the target person is sent 30 years in to the past. Joe gets rich and his life turns good until a day the mob decide to close the loop.

nodes.title: Inception
nodes.label: Inception
nodes.abstract: Cobb, a skilled thief who commits corporate espionage by infiltrating the subconscious of his targets is offered a chance to regain his old life as payment for a task considered to be impossible: "inception", the implantation of another person's idea into a target's subconscious.

nodes.title: The Mechanic
nodes.label: The Mechanic
nodes.abstract: Arthur Bishop (Statham) is a 'mechanic' - an elite assassin with a strict code and unique talent for cleanly eliminating targets. It's a job that requires professional perfection and total detachment, and Bishop is the best in the business. But when he is ordered to take out his mentor and close friend Harry (Sutherland), Bishop is anything but detached.

nodes.title: Bad Boys II
nodes.label: Bad Boys II
nodes.abstract: Mike Lowrey teams up with Marcus Bennett in order to fight the drug trafficking racket in Miami. Their investigation leads to a drug kingpin whose aspirations have started a covert war among the mobs. Mike starts getting close to Marcus' sister Syd, but the two cops have to go a long way before Mike can end up with Syd.

nodes.title: The November Man
nodes.label: The November Man
nodes.abstract: An ex- CIA operative is brought back in on a very personal mission and finds himself pitted against his former pupil in a deadly game involving high level CIA officials and the Russian president-elect.

nodes.title: The Man with the Iron Fists
nodes.label: The Man with the Iron Fists
nodes.abstract: In feudal China, a blacksmith who makes weapons for a small village is put in the position where he must defend himself and his fellow villagers.

nodes.title: Everly
nodes.label: Everly
nodes.abstract: An action/thriller centered on a woman who faces down assassins sent by her ex, a mob boss, while holed up in her apartment.

nodes.title: The Midnight Meat Train
nodes.label: The Midnight Meat Train
nodes.abstract: Leon is a photographer who lives with his girlfriend and waitress Maya. Leon is waiting for an opportunity to get into the photo business. With the help of their friend Jurgis through Maya, Leon fixes an appointment with Susan Hoff, the owner of an art gallery. But she asks Leon to improve more. Leon gets upset and comes on the streets taking random pictures with his camera.

nodes.title: Kite
nodes.label: Kite
nodes.abstract: Based on the groundbreaking, cult classic anime, KITE tells the story of Sawa, a young woman living in a corrupt society where crime and gangs terrorize the streets. When Sawa's mother and policeman father are found victims of a grisly double homicide, she begins a ruthless pursuit for the man who murdered them. With the help of her father's ex-partner, Karl Aker, and a mysterious friend from her past, she becomes a merciless teen assassin, blasting her way through the dark world of human trafficking only to uncover a devastating truth

nodes.title: Drive Angry
nodes.label: Drive Angry
nodes.abstract: Milton is a hardened felon who has broken out of Hell, intent on finding the vicious cult who brutally murdered his daughter and kidnapped her baby. He joins forces with Piper, a sexy, tough-as-nails waitress with a 69 Charger, who's also seeking redemption of her own. Caught in a deadly race against time, Milton has three days to avoid capture, avenge his daughter's death, and save her baby before she's mercilessly sacrificed by the cult.

nodes.title: Kick-Ass 2
nodes.label: Kick-Ass 2
nodes.abstract: The costumed high-school hero Kick-Ass joins with a group of normal citizens who have been inspired to fight crime in costume. Meanwhile, the Red Mist plots an act of revenge that will affect everyone Kick-Ass knows.

nodes.title: Miami Vice
nodes.label: Miami Vice
nodes.abstract: Miami Vice is an feature film based on the 1980's action drama TV series. The film tells the story of vice detectives Crockett and Tubbs and how their personal and professional lives are dangerously getting mixed.

nodes.title: Universal Soldier: Day of Reckoning
nodes.label: Universal Soldier: Day of Reckoning
nodes.abstract: John looks to take down Luc Deveraux after a home invasion claims his wife and daughter. The fight pits John against Andrew Scott and an army of genetically enhanced warriors; meanwhile, he must contend with a UniSol in relentless pursuit.

nodes.title: Machete
nodes.label: Machete
nodes.abstract: After being set-up and betrayed by the man who hired him to assassinate a Texas Senator, an ex-Federale launches a brutal rampage of revenge against his former boss.

nodes.title: Pusher
nodes.label: Pusher
nodes.abstract: A street dealer of London gets his life changed into worse within a course of a week on account of the fact that he had borrowed money from a supplier on a thing that is supposed to be assured but unfortunately it was not. The movie depicts the adverse situations that he faces after the borrowing along with how he fights them.

nodes.title: Knight and Day
nodes.label: Knight and Day
nodes.abstract: An action-comedy centered on a fugitive couple on a glamorous and sometimes deadly adventure where nothing and no one - even themselves - are what they seem. Amid shifting alliances and unexpected betrayals, they race across the globe, with their survival ultimately hinging on the battle of truth vs. trust.

nodes.title: 16 Blocks
nodes.label: 16 Blocks
nodes.abstract: An aging cop is assigned the ordinary task of escorting a fast-talking witness from police custody to a courthouse. There are however forces at work trying to stop prevent them from making it.

nodes.title: The Amazing Spider-Man
nodes.label: The Amazing Spider-Man
nodes.abstract: Peter Parker is an outcast high schooler was abandoned by his parents as a boy, leaving him to be raised by his Uncle Ben and Aunt May. Like most teenagers, Peter is trying to figure out who he is and how he got to be the person he is today. As Peter discovers a mysterious briefcase that belonged to his father, he begins a quest to understand his parents' disappearance—leading him directly to Oscorp and the lab of Dr. Curt Connors, his father's former partner. As Spider-Man is set on a collision course with Connors' alter ego, The Lizard, Peter will make life-altering choices to use his powers and shape his destiny to become a hero.

nodes.title: Lockout
nodes.label: Lockout
nodes.abstract: Set in the near future, Lockout follows a falsely convicted ex-government agent , whose one chance at obtaining freedom lies in the dangerous mission of rescuing the President's daughter from rioting convicts at an outer space maximum security prison.

nodes.title: 3 Days to Kill
nodes.label: 3 Days to Kill
nodes.abstract: A dangerous international spy is determined to give up his high stakes life to finally build a closer relationship with his estranged wife and daughter. But first, he must complete one last mission - even if it means juggling the two toughest assignments yet: hunting down the world's most ruthless terrorist and looking after his teenage daughter for the first time in ten years, while his wife is out of town.

nodes.title: Guardians of the Galaxy
nodes.label: Guardians of the Galaxy
nodes.abstract: Light years from Earth, 26 years after being abducted, Peter Quill finds himself the prime target of a manhunt after discovering an orb wanted by Ronan the Accuser.

nodes.title: The Wolverine
nodes.label: The Wolverine
nodes.abstract: Wolverine faces his ultimate nemesis - and tests of his physical, emotional, and mortal limits - in a life-changing voyage to modern-day Japan.

nodes.title: Memento
nodes.label: Memento
nodes.abstract: Suffering short-term memory loss after a head injury, Leonard Shelby embarks on a grim quest to find the lowlife who murdered his wife in this gritty, complex thriller that packs more knots than a hangman's noose. To carry out his plan, Shelby snaps Polaroids of people and places, jotting down contextual notes on the backs of photos to aid in his search and jog his memory. He even tattoos his own body in a desperate bid to remember.

nodes.title: Kiss of the Dragon
nodes.label: Kiss of the Dragon
nodes.abstract: A betrayed intelligence officer enlists the aid of a prostitute to prove his innocence from a deadly conspiracy while returning a favor to her.

nodes.title: Homefront
nodes.label: Homefront
nodes.abstract: Phil Broker is a former DEA agent who has gone through a crisis after his action against a biker gang went horribly wrong and it cost the life of his boss' son. He is recently widowed and is left with a 9-years-old daughter,Maddy. He decides to quit the turbulent and demanding life of thrill for Maddy's sake and retires to a small town. His daughter fights off a boy who was bullying her at school and this sets in motion a round of events that end in his direct confrontation with the local Meth drug lord. His past history with the biker gang also enters the arena, making matters more complex. But he has a mission in his mind to protect his daughter and he is ready to pay any cost that it demands.

nodes.title: Die Hard: With a Vengeance
nodes.label: Die Hard: With a Vengeance
nodes.abstract: John McClane is New York based investigator and he is again promptly back in the action mode. This time he is paired up with the regular civilian Zeus Carver in order to save the lives of innocent people. McClane now gets engaged into a new game as Simon drives him crazy.

nodes.title: Cop Out
nodes.label: Cop Out
nodes.abstract: Officers Jimmy Monroe and Paul Hodges have their weapons drawn on a gun-wielding killer. They agree to shoot on three. But, wait, does that mean 1…2… shoot or 1…2…3… then shoot? Punches hit hard and laughs hit harder (or is it the other way ’round?) when action star Bruce Willis and ace comic Tracy Morgan pair as bickering-but-got-your-back Brooklyn buddy cops. Kevin Smith (Clerks, Chasing Amy) directs the gritty, goofball goings-on as the guys hunt for a stolen 1952 mint condition baseball card (Jimmy needs it to fund his daughter’s wedding), a hunt plunging them into a gunslinging war with a deadly drug ring. Batter up, fans. The boys are ready to take you out to the ol’ brawl game!

nodes.title: Lock, Stock and Two Smoking Barrels
nodes.label: Lock, Stock and Two Smoking Barrels
nodes.abstract: Four Jack-the-lads find themselves heavily - seriously heavily - in debt to an East End hard man and his enforcers after a crooked card game. Overhearing their neighbours in the next flat plotting to hold up a group of out-of-their-depth drug growers, our heros decide to stitch up the robbers in turn. In a way the confusion really starts when a pair of antique double-barrelled shotguns go missing in a completely different scam.

nodes.title: From Paris with Love
nodes.label: From Paris with Love
nodes.abstract: While working at the American embassy in Paris, low-level intelligence agent James Reece gets involved in espionage when he's pulled into a terrorist plot by high-ranking but uncouth American operative Charlie Wax, who's trying to stop it.

nodes.title: Running Scared
nodes.label: Running Scared
nodes.abstract: This crime thriller is centered on drug dealer Joey. He must secure a drug deal that had gone horribly wrong. In the follow up, vicious characters are exposed that includes cops. Authority, the gang and the competition fight it out to claim their hands on the high value consignment.

nodes.title: Bad Boys
nodes.label: Bad Boys
nodes.abstract: Marcus Burnett is a hen-pecked family man. Mike Lowry is a foot-loose and fancy free ladies' man. Both are Miami policemen, and both have 72 hours to reclaim a consignment of drugs stolen from under their station's nose. To complicate matters, in order to get the assistance of the sole witness to a murder, they have to pretend to be each other.

nodes.title: Act of Valor
nodes.label: Act of Valor
nodes.abstract: Go 'down range' with real, active duty Navy SEALs in this adrenaline-fueled action-adventure that inserts you into the heart of the battle, alongside America's best and bravest. When a covert mission to rescue a kidnapped CIA operative uncovers a chilling plot, an elite, highly trained U.S. SEAL team speeds to hotspots around the globe, racing against the clock to stop a deadly terrorist attack.

nodes.title: The Equalizer
nodes.label: The Equalizer
nodes.abstract: In The Equalizer, Denzel Washington plays McCall, a man who believes he has put his mysterious past behind him and dedicated himself to beginning a new, quiet life. But when McCall meets Teri (Chloë Grace Moretz), a young girl under the control of ultra-violent Russian gangsters, he can’t stand idly by – he has to help her. Armed with hidden skills that allow him to serve vengeance against anyone who would brutalize the helpless, McCall comes out of his self-imposed retirement and finds his desire for justice reawakened. If someone has a problem, if the odds are stacked against them, if they have nowhere else to turn, McCall will help. He is The Equalizer.

nodes.title: MacGruber
nodes.label: MacGruber
nodes.abstract: MacGruber is an ex-special operative who is called back into action to take down Dieter Von Cunth, his anarchemy. The latter possesses a nuclear warhead and is stubborn on destroying Washington, DC. The movie progresses with interesting events and arouses much interest amongst its viewers.

nodes.title: Cat Run
nodes.label: Cat Run
nodes.abstract: Cat Run is the gripping tale of a single mother and hooker Cat who gets hired to be a part of an orgy for powerful men including an American Senator. All hell breaks loose when all the other girls get murdered so as to destroy all evidence involving the politicians. Only Cat manages to run along with the CD of evidence. This story is on whether or not Cat gets captured.

nodes.title: Alex Cross
nodes.label: Alex Cross
nodes.abstract: When the homicide detective Dr. Alex Cross is given his last assignment to track down the skilled sadistic killer, his life goes haywire. The killer named Picasso baits him and things get personal. But Cross is on the edge of sanity as he fights a villain more skilled than he is.

nodes.title: Max Payne
nodes.label: Max Payne
nodes.abstract: An assassin is out to take revenge for his sister's death and a DEA agent whose family members were killed due to a conspiracy come together to resolve a sequence of murders in New York. Both the assassin and DEA agent is hunted not only by the police but also by the ruthless corporation and the mob.

nodes.title: Savages
nodes.label: Savages
nodes.abstract: Pot growers Ben and Chon face off against the Mexican drug cartel who kidnapped their shared girlfriend.

nodes.title: Crank
nodes.label: Crank
nodes.abstract: Professional assassin Chev Chelios learns his rival has injected him with a poison that will kill him if his heart rate drops.

nodes.title: Empire
nodes.label: Empire
nodes.abstract: A big time drug dealer Victor Rosa is looking to get out of the game and sees his chance with a big deal with a new friend who happens to be a Wall St. stockbroker. Thinking this will be his chance to go out on top Victor soon finds out that he has been double crossed and his last option is to get revenge.

nodes.title: Next Day Air
nodes.label: Next Day Air
nodes.abstract: When two inept criminals get a package of cocaine, which is delivered to them, they feel overjoyed. The two of them think that they have hit the jackpot, several events happen after this incident and it changes the life of several individuals

nodes.title: Paid in Full
nodes.label: Paid in Full
nodes.abstract: An action movie of the emotional journey of a character Harleem who is victim of the 1980's drug scene and eventually create his own illegal empire which ends up to emotional crisis of conscience and dilemma within himself.

nodes.title: London Boulevard
nodes.label: London Boulevard
nodes.abstract: An ex-con hired to look after a reclusive young actress finds himself falling in love, which puts him in direct confrontation with one of London's most vicious gangsters.

nodes.title: Layer Cake
nodes.label: Layer Cake
nodes.abstract: A nameless cocaine dealer is planning for retirement after a very successful career' in the narcotics industry. But he is assigned one last job by his boss Jimmy Price. The task is to find Charlotte Ryder, the daughter of the millionaire businessman Edward. He accepts the assignment without knowing that it is going to put his life in jeopardy.

nodes.title: Easy Money
nodes.label: Easy Money
nodes.abstract: A three-tiered story centered around drugs and organized crime, and focused on a young man who becomes a runner for a coke dealer.

nodes.title: Out of the Furnace
nodes.label: Out of the Furnace
nodes.abstract: Rodney Baze disappears in a mysterious manner to which the police and the law figures are not much interested in dealing with. It is in this situation that the brother of this disappeared man Russell, takes matters under his own charge, thus seeking to make way for justice to be done to his own brother.

nodes.title: The Protector
nodes.label: The Protector
nodes.abstract: A young fighter named Kham must go to Australia to retrieve his stolen elephant. With the help of a Thai-born Australian detective, Kham must take on all comers, including a gang led by an evil woman and her two deadly bodyguards.

nodes.title: Hoodlum
nodes.label: Hoodlum
nodes.abstract: Black gangsters in 1930 Harlem fights Dutch Schultz who is trying to horn in on their numbers racket.

nodes.title: The Raid 2
nodes.label: The Raid 2
nodes.abstract: Rama is a faithful cop who undercover himself as a thug of Jakarta to unveil the corruption that has destroyed the image of the police force .Rama risk his wife and infant for the sake of his duty as he encounters the dangerous underworld criminals.

nodes.title: Punisher: War Zone
nodes.label: Punisher: War Zone
nodes.abstract: After hunting down and killing hundreds of violent criminals, Frank Castle, aka The Punisher, faces his most deadly foe yet: Jigsaw. |

nodes.title: Friday the 13th
nodes.label: Friday the 13th
nodes.abstract: In this 12th installment of friday 13th, A group of young adults discover a boarded up Camp Crystal Lake, where they soon encounter Jason Voorhees (Mears) and his deadly intentions.

nodes.title: A Million Ways to Die in the West
nodes.label: A Million Ways to Die in the West
nodes.abstract: As a cowardly farmer begins to fall for the mysterious new woman in town, he must put his new-found courage to the test when her husband, a notorious gun-slinger, announces his arrival.

nodes.title: Immortals
nodes.label: Immortals
nodes.abstract: Theseus is a mortal man chosen by Zeus to lead the fight against the ruthless King Hyperion, who is on a rampage across Greece to obtain a weapon that can destroy humanity.

nodes.title: Seven Psychopaths
nodes.label: Seven Psychopaths
nodes.abstract: Marty Faranan, a struggling writer aspires to complete his first screenplay. Billy Bickle is his best friend and an unemployed actor. Billy and hid partner, Hans, steal a gangster's dog to demand money from the owner. However, the gangster kidnaps Marty and Hans unless he is told about his pet's whereabouts.

nodes.title: Wanted
nodes.label: Wanted
nodes.abstract: Wesley is a guy who has grown up without his father. One day he learns that his father is an assassin. After his father is mysteriously killed he is recruited by the secret organization that recruited his father. He is trained to be a fine assassin and told to follow the footsteps of his father. But it is not as easy as it looks.

nodes.title: Bad Lieutenant
nodes.label: Bad Lieutenant
nodes.abstract: While investigating a young nun's rape, a corrupt New York City police detective, with a serious drug and gambling addiction, tries to change his ways and find forgiveness.

nodes.title: Four Brothers
nodes.label: Four Brothers
nodes.abstract: Four brothers have come together to seek revenge of the death of their mother. It apparently seems that their mother is killed in a robbery of grocery store but more secrets come into light as the brothers investigate about the death of their mother. One of them is associated with the local gangster.

nodes.title: Fast & Furious
nodes.label: Fast & Furious
nodes.abstract: When a crime brings them back to L.A., fugitive ex-con Dom Toretto reignites his feud with agent Brian O'Conner. But as they are forced to confront a shared enemy, Dom and Brian must give in to an uncertain new trust if they hope to outmaneuver him. And the two men will find the best way to get revenge: push the limits of what's possible behind the wheel.

nodes.title: Walking Tall
nodes.label: Walking Tall
nodes.abstract: A former U.S. soldier returns to his hometown to find it overrun by crime and corruption, which prompts him to clean house.

nodes.title: Fast Five
nodes.label: Fast Five
nodes.abstract: Dominic and his crew find themselves on the wrong side of the law once again as they try to switch lanes between a ruthless drug lord and a relentless federal agent.

nodes.title: Faster
nodes.label: Faster
nodes.abstract: A story of a lone man recently released from prison who seeks out revenge from the people in his past responsible for his imprisonment. He realises he isnt the only one wanting to settle old scores. He also realises that vengeance has a price to pay, damage to his immortal soul. Will he succeed

nodes.title: Grosse Pointe Blank
nodes.label: Grosse Pointe Blank
nodes.abstract: Martin Blank is an ace hit-man who suddenly decides that he's had enough of all the violence and killing. While Martin makes plans to attend his high school reunion, he discovers that leaving his past life behind is not as easy as he thought as other assassin is sent to settle scores with Martin.

nodes.title: Waist Deep
nodes.label: Waist Deep
nodes.abstract: When paroled ex-convict O2's son is kidnapped, he forces street vendor Coco to help him out. Meanwhile drug lord Meat declares he has junior and demands $100,000. Coco and O2 then chalk out a plan to put the pimp P-Money and Meat's gangs against each other and steal their money.

nodes.title: Saw III
nodes.label: Saw III
nodes.abstract: Jigsaw kidnaps a doctor to keep him alive while he watches his new apprentice put an unlucky citizen through a brutal test.

nodes.title: John Wick
nodes.label: John Wick
nodes.abstract: After the sudden death of his beloved wife, John Wick receives one last gift from her, a beagle puppy named Daisy, and a note imploring him not to forget how to love. But John's mourning is interrupted when his 1969 Boss Mustang catches the eye of sadistic thug Iosef Tarasov who breaks into his house and steals it, beating John unconscious in the process. Unwittingly, he has just reawakened one of the most brutal assassins the underworld has ever known.
